Showroom Sales Consultants for a luxury retail store
Confidential Company - ,
Date Posted: 2014/04/30 07:02:54
Ref. JB3045721
Job Description
Job Description
Attend and greet customers at the store
Assist customers in product selection understanding their requirements and choice of product
Maintain the display and clean, appealing presentation of products in the showroom
Research and stay up-to-date on product knowledge and industry trends
Use strong consultative sales skills, and interpersonal skills, attention to detail, strong follow-up skills and motivation to make the sale
Track customer returns
Maintain accurate and organized customer files
Schedule deliveries
Assist in scheduled physical inventory counts, if need be
Coordinate receiving and delivery of products in a timely manner
Use appropriate office technologies and computers to process and track orders and maintain excellent communication with all contacts, internally and externally
Attend all internal and external training programs organized by the company
Skills
Only FEMALE candidate must apply
Immediate joining required
CV must carry recent picture. CVs without pics will not be accepted
Preference shall be given to Russians / Chinese / Arabic speaking
